## Educational Use Notice

This educational platform is dedicated to promoting constitutional literacy
and civic awareness in India. The content is intended for educational 
purposes and is aligned with the constitutional values of justice, liberty,
equality, and fraternity as enshrined in the Constitution of India.

## Attribution

This project draws inspiration from the vision of Dr. B.R. Ambedkar and 
the founding fathers of the Indian Constitution. Educational content is 
based on publicly available constitutional documents and legal frameworks.

## Disclaimer

While every effort has been made to ensure accuracy, this platform is for
educational purposes only and should not be considered as legal advice.
For official constitutional interpretation, please refer to authoritative
legal sources and the Supreme Court of India's judgments.